title: Music Festival Clothing: Fringe | Lord & Taylor
description:
Music festival season 2015 is upon us and we’re ramping up our music festival clothing.  Our festival outfits are inspired by fringe.  We love spotting fringe boots, vests, dresses, and handbags across the festival scene.  Explore Lord & Taylor’s Design Lab for fringe and more festival clothing ideas.  

Shop Now: http://bit.ly/music-festival-outfits
